nodes.text: Zero Zero Zero is an article written by Morrie Mullins as a tie in to the Living Force adventure Decision: Coruscant. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on November 4, 2004 and took the form of a speech by Senator Lavina Durada-Vashne Wren to the people of the Cularin system explaining her efforts to secure military aid for the system and its subsequent refusal by the Galactic Senate.
